Aṅguttara Nikāya 10 
13. Parisuddhavagga 
131. Navamasutta 
“Dasayime, bhikkhave, dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā ekantanibbidāya virāgāya nirodhāya upasamāya abhiññāya sambodhāya nibbānāya saṃvattanti, nāññatra sugatavinayā. 
Katame dasa? 
Sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāvimutti—
ime kho, bhikkhave, dasa dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā ekantanibbidāya virāgāya nirodhāya upasamāya abhiññāya sambodhāya nibbānāya saṃvattanti, nāññatra sugatavinayā”ti. 
Navamaṃ. 
